summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to land use and zoning amending Plat 34E, Page 99, of the Official Zoning Map of The City of Seattle (Ordinance 86300) to rezone certain property in Block 17, Supplemental Plat of G. Kinnear's Addition to the City of Seattle from Multiple Residence Low Density (RM 800) Zone to Community Business (BC) Zone.
